        <Param val="Instructions &amp;#10;You’ll see pictures of hand shapes on one side of the screen. When the green dot comes, make the hand shape using the same side of your body. When the red dot comes, relax your hand. Keep looking at the dot in the middle." valType="str" updates="constant" name="text"/>
